  stepText: "To aim, press grab button to lock the striker.\r\nYour wrist band glows
    green to confirm proper aim mode.\r\nYou\u2019ll also see an aim arrow on the
    striker. Rotate your wrist to align this arrow with the glowing guide arrow,
    then press trigger to strike.\r\nNow you try it. "
